so things are going pretty good.. im still working at both the gas station and the hardware store but im thinking about putting in my 2 weeks at the hardware store. becasue the gas station is going to give me more hours and a raise!

so pretty sure I thought girls were soupose to be confusing .. not guys ?! 

maybe I just have major guy problems?

what a bunch of haters .. grrr

big news !!! 

my car is offically done ! im soooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo happy I can drive again 
I passed emissions and got my sticker thing today .. tomorrow me and kim and my sisters are going to go to a haunted house im super excited !!! 

i got a letter in the mail today from mel .. it was so awesome to hear from her .. everything is going good .. im so happy for her .. and I cant wait till I leave !

riding my bike to work in the hot hot heat
and in the freezing cold in the same week .. only in wisconsin 

so all my tickets are offically paid .. I got a letter in the mail that said I can get my DL back and mailed it in .. so I should have it by monday .

frank and I went and got my car from my moms and its now in my driveway ... now just have to look for a hood ..frank thinks he might have  found one .. so cross your fingers ! 

wyatt and i are stuck at home for the second day in a row .. at least I have someone to talk to ?!

iv worked the past 16 days in a row and I have till my birthday weekend before I have off .. you do the math 

i lost my ambition to write 

its not like anyone cares

so tomorrow i have an interview for a 3rd job .. im seriously thinking about taking it .. but im going to see what they have to offer first. im excited 

i want to have a bon-fire and just have a bunch of people over and chill and smoke and camp outside in tents and i would make breakfast in the morning .. wouldnt that be cool ?!

my birthday is comming up november 19th bitches ..its so weird i'll be 20 no more teens!.. I didnt even realize it .. i'll have to do something for that too. Im not sure how im going to out due myself for the bomb party denyse and I had last year for my golden .. i'll have to think of something awesome .. I wish I have a crap load of $$ like all those rich assholes on mysweet sixteen so I could throw a mad party .. but im just a poor white girl and I totally dont have 129347029 friends.

so things are getting better .. i have 2 jobs now .. working at bills gas station and at ace hardware .. so im pulling in 60 hours a week .. hard to imagine for a person who dosent have a car or a drivers licence ! but its working so far ! so i think by the middle of november i'll be out of debt which is so awesome ! other wise things are pretty normal again .. chill at home .. watch wyatt sit here .. dont really hang out much becasue no one wants to ever come out here or anything .. but whatever guess just shows u who your "real friends" are .. not very many people ! sad but true 

xoxo 
-rae

so i had a pretty good weekend 
saturday frank wyatt and I went to kalebs game then took him to meet his dad 
then the 3 of us did a little shopping. i pick out this super cute outfit for wyatt :) 
came home and chilled for a bit i washed franks truck then we went on a motercycle ride it was so much fun !! later that night Denyse came over .. I was so happy to see here. it just sucked becasue we were both tired. we ended up going to see a movie in waukesha we saw  the excorsim of emily rose .. it was creepy but very good :) i was bummed that we didnt get to spend more time together but hopefully we'll get to hang out again soon ! 

sunday I pretty much just sat around all day .. went shopping with frank .. it was so effin hot outand he wouldnt turn on the air . he finally did today :) i felt sick again last night so i tryed taking a nap at like 6 and slept till allmost 8 and went back to bed around 11 .. I donno why iv been feeling sick for no reason lately . its kinda weird !?.. oh well im better now

no plans really for this week .. looking for a job 
maybe hanging out with kim and luke this weekend . fri and sat i hope 

thats about it !!

xoxo 
rae

friday night kim came over and picked me up we ended up going back to her place .. her dd was having a bon fire so we sat their for a little while trying to gind something to do luke came over and chilled with us. at like 10:30 she got a call from her ex boyfriends loser brother, he was stuck on the east side his bike broke or something and was leaking oil. so luke kimmy and I went on an adventure. on the way down luke tanked some beers. we got thier and this kid was going to take us to some party on warren st. but the only problem was none of us knew where the eff warren st was ?! .. so I mad the mistake of asking someone "do you know where warren is?" .. and I got the simple minded answer of "warren who" .. my bad I forgot to say warren st ! so we just ended up taking this kid home and the 3 of us went back to kims to enjoy the bon fire. then korin comes over like 30min later and brings a bunch of carrol boys .. so we all get tanked. and luke and I end up pushing eachother on the tree swing .. then laying in the hammock together. weird !? finally its like 10 to 3am .. so luke goes home and kim and I go to mickey d's but for some crazy reason its closed. so we think maybe tbell is open to 3am .. well it was . so we ordered pull up to pay .. and the chick starts screaming .. and going crazy .. were like wtf !? .. she runs away and this other guy comes and i guess we ran over a sauce packet and it shot her in the eye! what are the effin odds of that happening ?!! crazy shit. so we get to my house and I ended up never falling asleep , kim was on the phone till like 5am amy called me atr 4:30 .. I had to get up at 8 and babysit! yesterday we just chilled went shopping .. post-it noted lukes car while he was at work .. then hung out at his apartment. today im going to a family bon fire thing in wind lake and tomorrow is the demoderby with elliot .. im so excited I cant wait ! here are some pics... my arm is still killin me and i havent revieved any love notes .. im quite sad:( kim kim lukes car !!! my arm day #2

so I just got stung by an effin be .. wtf ? I wasnt even bothering it .. I was taking the babys for a walk and a stupid bee stings me . gosh IDIOT ! look at my arm it hurts ;( .. please send cards and flowers my poor arm
so im babysitting .. my new little cousin wyatt and my new little puppy ally ... their both 3 months old ally is 2days older here are some pics. Cutie's and me ...

so today was okay .. got up early took nick for a jog finished up my laundry and chilled for most of the day .. kimmy came over around 6 and took me to get my check we ended up going to mayfair so I could look for this shirt my sister wanted didnt find it :( . but I got to see dave it was nice we talked for a bit and it was very good to see him again. went to target and visited some old friends and chilled at kims house for a while 

I guess friday were all going to try to get together and do something I suguested bowling since thats what we used to do .. then sat chillin with d ... I cant wait ! i have to try to find a job i hope that works out okay otherwise not much new 

xoxo 
rae

so im home now and I feel better allready .. things are looking good and im excited to get my life back on track. so much has changed in the 3 months that I was gone, the baby , we have a horse and were getting another one and a new puppy named ally she is so cute and I couldnt be happier :) 

xoxo 
rae

im going home today . kinda suck becasue now I have to quit my job and fide something differet I cant stand it here anymore I am not a slave its not my fault I couldnt sleep last night or at all this month maybe it has to do with the fact that I sleep on a matress on the basement floor becasue my mom is a cunt . I dont care what anyone has to say my mom dosent love me she could care less if I was alive. I hate being treated like a worthless piece of shit. so im leaving. im going home and getting my life back together no more of this I cat take it

this not being able to sleep thing is really starting to suck 

I work monday and tuesday 3-11
if anyone wants to hang out I can try but remember I have no car 

i want to cuddle :(

i dont even know how im feeling .. so unwanted ..by everyone 
I seriously think im going to move back in with frank . change my number and not talk to anyone anymore im so sick of all the stupid drama . im sick of being used

not much new .. found out today that Im going to cancun for x-mas .. sounds interesting . drinking age is 18 so im for sure getting trashed this is probally going to be a fun time I hope .. and I might be able to bring some one .. my last awesome vacation was to new york on my 18th birthday with my best friend. I wish she would come with me on this trip. she is the only person I would ever want to go on a vacation with. god i miss the fun times. so went today and applyed for some more jobs. might be working at citgo on howell and ryan 3rd shift. pns sucks. but whatever. tomorrow thirsty thursdays . not drinking but hanging out with mel should be some good times!!!.. hey mel call me before you go to work tomorrow so we can figure stuff out ! this weekend is the racine county fair .. phil vasser on sat might go with the waukesha crew or just hang with them on friday who knows !? got ditched again today .. im over it I just hung out with my mom and went to the bar and drank with missy. other wise nothing new . still clean . my shitty car is still shitty im still poor and keeping my head up ! rock on RAE ! xoxo rae

so its been a month and a half .. im proud of myself 
I finally have a temp job . working at pick 'n save on hwy 100 untill I find something better. I decided that im only staying at my moms till heather goes back to school then im moving back home and going to school. my mom bought me a new car .. its a piece of shit but its just temp untill I find something better or frank fixes my accord. 

I havent been home in a month it kinda sucks I miss frank and my bed and I wouldnt mind seeing the baby. I still havent been doing much of anything . the whole randy thing was good while it lasted but it over now and he turned into an asshole like all other guys . so I think im going to take a break . 

tomorrow im going to hang out with kimmy im glad i miss her we always had fun . and I might see if I can get my job back at target i donno for sure yet. well I guess thats about it. I still think about everyone of you all the time. it sucks being the outsider but i did it to myself

im depressed , i need a job soooooooo bad 
i feel so useless sitting at home every day all day.. all night doing nothing 
it sucks 
I hate it 
I want it to end

so yesterday I took my mom to work in the morning so I could try once again to find a job .. applyed at a few places came home and cleaned and hung out with my sister . pick my mom back up from work came home and randy came and picked me up. we went to get his pictures developed and then went back to his place. we ended up doing laundry, we went through old photos together, watched dukes of hazards, went back to pick his pictures up, went mudding, back to his house. and pretty much passed out. i felt bad becasue he had to work this morning so he had to take me home before he went to work. and of course he woke up late. so I got home at like 5:30am .. and slept till 12. still sick, bored I donno dont really talk to any one any more .. amy has been too busy with steve this past week . still sucks not having a car even more not having a job. pretty much sit home everyday, go to my sisters softball games. clean. get bitched at it sucks but im over it I guess. I relize I dont deserve anything good any more . I know I screwed up and I cant fix things. everyday I still think about how things used to be . hangning out with my best friend, no cares in the world. and I threw it all away for no reason . I have nothing to show for it. I really want to get my shit together, get my car fixed, a job . new friends . and just start over. I feel I am a different person now (again) and im not going to make the same mistakes I did last time. im learning I just hope I can succeed

so since last weekend I have been seeing someone new .. his name is randy larson, he is 22 and perfect. i met him through amys new boyfriend steve who is also awesome. 6 of us went camping on friday and had a blast! saturday morning randy took me fishing it was cute

today im sick. I ended up staying hom last night while all of them went out. I would have gone but it was probally better that I got some rest. randy call me on his way home to check on me. 

i hope we get to hang out today .. I know he has to work on his truck but not sure what else I just dont want to be stuck at home all day ..

so here is my update 
came to waukesha yesterday for the baby shower, the baby was born 5 weeks early and 
is now 15 days old he is so very cute. so I ended up having some old friends from target come 
over kimmy, bob , ryan , and lando .. then we stoped over at emilys d. and hung out with her and chap 
for a while it was nice to finally hang out with different people. 

bennett and I broke up, which I think is good .. but its crazy david wants me so bad 
and I dont know what to do ? other wise everything is looking up .. I just need to find a job .. 
I have been clean from blow for 3 weeks .. iv been getting counsling im a little happier other then 
that not much going on .. im staying with my mom. I help at bennetts house just about every day with 
cleaning stalls and letting the horses out and then chill at home with my lil sister.

bored .. start my new job tomorrow i'll be working monday thru friday 3pm to 11:30pm .. sat and sunday off which is nice 

waiting to go back out to waukesha, I got a call from frank today and amy is in the hospital I guess something to do with she has high blood pressure so she has to have the baby 4 weeks early so im going up thier to be with them and make sure everthing is okay 

partying has been fun but im honestly getting sick of it, and all the money it cost. with moving and this new job I want to try to get back on my feet. 

im happy with bennett but its so hard with him still having feelings for his ex and working with her and talking to her it sucks . it makes him act like an asshole and me be a bitch. its so hard iv become so attached and how could I not he was the niciest to me. he called me everyday , the sex was awesome, he would go to work and get off at 4am and come home and crawl in bed with me I donno everything was perfect and now it seems to be going down hill and im scared

its truely been a long time 
today is bennetts 21 birthday, last night we had a blast and comming home was even better. we slept till like 1pm I was soupose to start one of my new jobs today but I got it switched to tomorrow ! and the other one I start on thursday. 

im now living with my mom again so I can be with bennett things are nice and I can honestly say he does make me happy. I miss all the kids from target im going to have to plan some kind of get together soon. well jeffs here to pick us up and i didnt take a shower yet so I better fly 

xoxo 
rae

I think things are getting better 
amy fianlly broke up with kyle im so happy for her she is going on a "date" today with this joe guy that she has liked since 4th grade he seems really cool and that he will treat her like the world. 

I met another guy online he lives in minnesota, iv been talking to him for like almost a month online and like everday this week on the phone. he makes me happy and thats all I want is to be happy and smile. he seems like a dream. I dont want to rush things becasue I want this one to work. everytime I talk about him or i am talking to him I get butterflys and I have this feeling like things would work out really good between us. i hope im right. im making sure before hand that my heart dosent get broken again and that he dosent turn out to be another jesse. im finally realizing where I went wrong with him so im being extra carefull that hes not the same way. 

i want to move out I think its time, im going to start saving my money and looking for another job. i love target but its not cutting it anymore. i love my new car its so me. 

iv been hanging out with my cousin alot lately, its fun I know he cares about me witch makes me happy becasue I havent had that feeling from someone in a long time. but I know he'll be there for me whenever I need him. 

sorry if I havent really been talking to anyone lately iv been trying to keep it low key. and it seem like everyone is doing the same. I relize now we are all going our seprate ways. i still care about everyone of you, and I hope you know any time you ever need anything all you have to do is call . even if its just to talk. 

well im out .. sorry this is soo long but its been a while since Iv had a meaningful update 

xoxo 
rae

I believe the sun should never set upon an argument I believe we place our happiness in other people's hands I believe that junk food tastes so good because it's bad for you I believe your parents did the best job they knew how to do I believe that beauty magazines promote low self-esteem I believe I'm loved when I'm completely by myself alone I believe in karma what you give is what you get returned I believe you can't appreciate real love till you've been burned I believe the grass is no more greener on the other side I believe you don't know what you've got until you say goodbye I believe you can't control or choose your sexuality I believe that trust is more important than monogamy I believe your most attractive features are your heart and soul I believe that family is worth more than money or gold I believe the struggle for financial freedom is unfair I believe the only ones who disagree are millionaires I believe forgiveness is the key to your unhappiness I believe that wedded bliss negates the need to be undressed I believe that God does not endorse TV evangelists I believe in love surviving death into eternity

So I made it through the first month of the year I wonder what will happen next month ?!?! [recap of January]in no specific order I have worked over 300 hours this month alone. my car broke so I spent $100 and got it fixed and then it broke again 3 days later so now I have to buy a new one. I got a raise. i've lost 20lbs .. most of it was probally due to the fact that I was sick for 3+ weeks. not sure what else I cant really think right now. iv worked the past 7 days in a row I had to wake up this morning at 4:30am to be to work by 6am ..it was fun im glad I went I always have fun at work . i guess im weird.. I dont have off till friday and I think I close everyday this week so i probally will only be leaving my house to go to and from work. frank found a car for me I guess a 94' honda accord (white).. I dont know if I want it yet .. but he said if I dont he's still going to buy it for himself and sell the sunbird ?! so I donno ?!

so its been like a flipping week and a half and i keep thinking im getting better but im not, I keep getting sicker. I have never been this sick for so long in my life EVER ! its so gay. so I have pretty much been doing nothing for the past week .. sleep.work.sit at home. I havent even went to the bar after work. yesterday I finally ate something it was like the first time I could eat in the past 7 days. whatever im dont complaining no one cares anyways. 

I have to go get ready for work . peace out
